  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.fw.yapool.listener.PoolListener

    BoundQueryCache

    public class SimpleQueryCache
extends PoolListener
implements IQueryCache
    A simple IQueryCache that also has the option to update some QueryCacheStats.

    Fred
